page_description: Use this article to learn about using the available web app to chat with Azure OpenAI models.
chunk_content: Deleting your Cosmos DB instanceDeleting your web app does not delete your Cosmos DB instance automatically. To delete your Cosmos DB instance along with all stored chats, you need to go to the associated resource in the Azure portal and delete it. If you delete the Cosmos DB resource but keep the chat history option turned on in the studio, your users are notified of a connection error but can continue to use the web app without access to the chat history.
